Q: What is GAE BOILERTPLATE?
Google App Engine Boilerplate is one of the best tools to create your own powerful project on App Engine (Python) 
and is available completely free of charge under the GPLv2 (or later) license. Enjoy!

Q: Where to download?
http://www.linkedin.com/groups/Google-App-Engine-Boilerplate-20-128878.S.135560316
https://github.com/coto/gae-boilerplate
http://appengine.beecoss.com/

